  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Confucius
Lived:         551 - -479
Nationality:   Chinese
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Confucianism
Contribution:  Ren, li, filial piety; still shapes East Asian society 2,500 years later
Quote:         "It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop."

Name:          Albert Einstein
Lived:         1879 - 1955
Nationality:   German-American
Field:         Physics
Known For:     Theory of Relativity
Contribution:  E=mc2; photoelectric effect; special and general relativity
Quote:         "Imagination is more important than knowledge."

Name:          Isaac Newton
Lived:         1643 - 1727
Nationality:   English
Field:         Physics/Math
Known For:     Laws of Motion, Gravity
Contribution:  Principia Mathematica; invented calculus; explained planetary motion
Quote:         "If I have seen further, it is by standing on the shoulders of giants."

